Commands tested: `audit`, `risk`, `status`, `network`, `diagnose`, `scan`, `ghosts`

### Finding #5: Handoff overstates completion

Acknowledged. This sprint does NOT claim the full `/goal` is met. The remaining gap is the interactive return path (item 6 in the plan).

